  "title": "EEG-attention-rsvp-exp1",
  "description": "EEG dataset from Experiment 1 of Grootswagers et al. (2021) investigating neural dynamics of task-relevant information prioritization. Participants performed a rapid serial visual presentation (RSVP) task with small letters presented on large objects while EEG was recorded. This dataset provides raw electrophysiological recordings to examine how the brain prioritizes behaviorally relevant stimuli during visual attention tasks.",
